  19+ 2000              BORDCR          equ     $5C48                   // BORDCR system variable
  20+ 2000              FLAGS2          equ     $5C6A                   // for caps-lock
  21+ 2000              RAMTOP          equ     $5CB2
  22+ 2000              TSTACK          equ     $5C00                   // TSTACK
  23+ 2000              // FSTACK          ecu     $4000 - 8
