  60+ 2000              //  ______________________________________________________________________
  61+ 2000              //
  62+ 2000              //  Inner interpreter next-address pointer. This is 2T-state faster than "jp address"
  63+ 2000              next            macro
  64+ 2000 ~                            jp      (ix)
  65+ 2000                              endm
  66+ 2000
  67+ 2000              psh1            macro
  68+ 2000 ~                            push    hl
  69+ 2000 ~                            jp      (ix)
  70+ 2000                              endm
