 177++23CB              //  ______________________________________________________________________
 178++23CB              //
 179++23CB              // f_open       a1 a2 b -- u f
 180++23CB              // open a file
 181++23CB              // a1 (filespec) is a null-terminated string, such as produced by ," definition
 182++23CB              // a2 is address to an 8-byte header data used in some cases.
 183++23CB              // b is access mode-byte, that is a combination of:
 184++23CB              // any/all of:
 185++23CB              //   esx_mode_read          $01 request read access
