  78+ 3201              // vocabulary   -- cccc     ( compile time )
  79+ 3201              // Defining word used in the form   VOCABULARY cccc
  80+ 3201              // creates the word  cccc  that gives the name to the vocabulary.
  81+ 3201              // Giving  cccc  makes the vocabulary CONTEXT so its words are executed first
  82+ 3201              // Giving  cccc DEFINITIONS makes  the vocabulary  CURRENT
